txt.en: You have been tasked with defeating the Hill Giant, Svalfang, in the Wildwood.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Radhril for your reward!

'Would you accompany me on a mission, [placeholder]?

'The Free Peoples in the Wildwood have reported the giant, Svalfang, wandering through the Wildwood. There are reports of trees and boulders ripped from the ground. I believe this Svalfang is not in a pleasant mood.

'If the Wildwood is ever to be peaceful, Svalfang will need to be driven away.'
Svalfang the Hill Giant ventures into the Wildwood, seeking payment for those he has killed.\n\nYour mission is to defeat the hill giant, Svalfang, in the Wildwood.
Some monsters in this mission will attempt a crushing attack, wounding and stunning anyone hit.
Your mission is to defeat the hill giant, Svalfang, in the Wildwood.\n\nSpeak to Radhril.
'We have done well, [placeholder]. With Svalfang defeated, perhaps the giant now understands that the Wildwood is no place for ruthless giants.'
